COMMAND NAME  : Cleric Variable Set  | Cleric Variable Unset
COMMAND SYNTAX: Cset <var> <value>   | Cunset <var>
COMMAND COST  : None                 | None
DESCRIPTION   : These commands allow you to set certain Cleric variables that
                affect certain aspects of your life as a Cleric. To see the
                available variables, do 'Info variables'. To see the value
		of all variables, use the Cset command without arguments.
